,{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip/accessibilityAction(named:_:)-57t4n":{"title":"accessibilityAction(named:_:)","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip\/accessibilityaction(named:_:)-57t4n","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/accessibilityAction(named:_:)-57t4n","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"accessibilityAction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"named","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10Foundation23LocalizedStringResourceV","text":"LocalizedStringResource","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", () -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> "